len thing recite 2 rakat namaz like fajr with the intention of getting back the stolen thing. After namaz recite 70-70 times YAA MU’EE-DO and blow right and left, front and back and then recite this dua. Some people say that this ritual (amal) has been tried and tested…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Chori shudah ashya (cheezo’n) ki talaash ke liye 2 rakat namaz (Fajr ki tarah) padhe’n is niyyat se keh chori shudah maal ya cheez waapas mil jaaye. Namaz ke baad daae’n baae’n (right left) aur aaghe peechhe 70-70 martaba YAA MU’EE-DO ka vird kare aur us ke baad yeh dua padhe. Baaz afraad ka qoul hai keh yeh mujarrab (aazmaayi huwi) hai…", "UrduDescription": "چوری شدہ اشیاء کی تلاش کے لئے ۲ رکعت نماز پڑھیں اس نیت سے کہ چوری شدہ مال یا چیز واپس مل جائے، نماز کے بعد دائیں بائیں اور آگے پیچھے 70-70 مرتبہ ’’یَا مُعِیْدُ‘‘ کا ورد کرے اور اس کے بعد یہ دعا پڑھے بعض افراد کا قول ہے کہ یہ مجرب ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText1